Package org.zoolu.sip.call

Interface Summary
CallListener Interface CallListener can be implemented to manage SIP calls (sipx.call.Call).
ExtendedCallListener Interface ExtendedCallListener can be implemented to manage exteded SIP calls (sipx.call.ExtendedCall).
 

Class Summary
Call Class Call implements SIP calls.
CallListenerAdapter Class CallListenerAdapter implements CallListener interface providing a dummy implementation of all Call callback functions used to capture Call events.
ExtendedCall Class ExtendedCall extends basic SIP calls.
SdpTools Class SdpTools collects some static methods for managing SDP materials.
